 *==========================================================================*
 * Quick Note:                                                              * 
 * JKv 13.12.2017: In the manual version, dw_dw.QUALITATIVE_JUDGEMENT is    * 
 * selecting where expire_date>=active_date of any information_date. In     * 
 * the definition (in a code comment) it is said: "pd_class_cd from the     * 
 * table “QUALITATIVE_ANSWERS” at the same information date as in  the      * 
 * ACCOUNT_EXP-table if there exists a valid qualitative judgment at the    * 
